{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong># Questions, Doubts... Truth!</strong></h2>&quot;What if robots gained free will? Would they still exist for humanity's sake?&quot;<br>In 2030, a world where robots and humans coexist faces a chilling series of murders!<br>The prime suspects? Robots living among us.<br>Unearth the scattered evidence at crime scenes,<br>and navigate through the web of truth and deception in the robots' testimonies.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2492290/extras/616x346.png?t=1728367860\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong># No Choices, Only Questions.</strong></h2>Your questions are the keys to unraveling the case.<br>All victims are linked to an experiment called &quot;Project Atlas.&quot;<br>Subject X, Atlas Chip, and H.R.P.<br>What massive truth is hidden behind this chain of events?<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2492290/extras/Honeycam_2024-05-31_18-33-44__1_.gif?t=1728367860\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong># Game Features</strong></h2>- Experience 5 gripping episodes.<br>- Engage in deep conversations with case-related robots to uncover the incident's full story and crucial clues.<br>- If the suspect robot is the culprit, trigger system overload questions to switch them to confession mode, revealing the incident's truth.<br>- Discover hidden stories by finding all evidence and confirming the case's truth.<br>- Utilize the investigation status board actively to ensure you don't miss any vital clues or decisive questions.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2492290/extras/UncoverTheSmokingGun-2024-07-12-17-31-14.gif?t=1728367860\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"The Mansion, Case Closed","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2492290/7bc1d717a22d59f594d98aaf48d018e642a8fb88.jpg"},{"name":"Eviden